Package com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.client Description

SitesWrapper Application Presentation Layer Network is a state of the art platform and network independent presentation system which leverages the entire spectrum of Google technologies to manage information and business process in order to provide management, the workforce and customers what they need to make and implement decisions easily, efficiently and effectively.
To Do:
Add Google Adwords Display Network Capability
Enables SitesWrapper to take part in the Google Display Network
Add Google YouTube Direct Capability
Enables URLeSties to customize and display and solicit submission of YouTube videos.
Classes in this package handle client side communications, presentation and application logic associated with the web application.

UI contains client side application code.

Rpc is responsible for handling the client side of all RPC based inter-process communications.

RpcAsync handles the asynchronous call back component of GWT RPC.

Since:
1.0
